DELIVERY REQUIREMENTS
One Markdown report per document
One CSV covering all extracted items
Preserve document order
Never omit explicitly stated content
If you want next, I can:
add a “safeguard-derived outcome” flag
split development vs environmental/social outcomes
or tune this for World Bank / ADB harmonization
